The idea behind Pumpkin Palooza is an event for
lovers of all things pumpkin. Pumpkin has become
more than just a halloween ornament. Now
consumers are surrounded with anything from
various pumpkin spice lattes to pumpkin pie
flavoured ice cream. With the pumpkin industry
growing every year its a surprised nothing like
Pumpkin Palooza has happened before. Sponsored
by Starbucks, Dairy Queen, Body Shop, Party
Packagers and many more, Pumpkin Palooza will
have plenty of different pumpkin related activities
and snacks. If you love pumpkin, this is the place to
be. Bring the family!
Aimed at middle to middle-high class families with
kids under the age of 18 who enjoy going out and
doing family activities. It is aimed to keep the kids
entertained while also mainly appealing to the
mothers, but with a few fatherly things as well.
